{"lastModified":1751989404169,"uri":"c::25969204094::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1","yachtType":["Sailing","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nYAZZ is a classically styled, but modern yacht launched by Aegean Yacht in 2007. With vast social areas, extensive toys, an attentive crew and even a resident DJ, this yacht offers the perfect platform for entertaining. Offering you the best of both, YAZZ delivers vintage style and excellent service alongside modern systems and facilities, all aimed to provide maximum guest enjoyment.\n\nUpon entering the main saloon, you are met with a vibrant and eclectic mix of colours, furnishings and artwork. Despite its large size, the main saloon remains an exceptionally warm and inviting indoor area to come and relax. Heading below to the lower deck, you will find all five guest staterooms. There are two full-beam master staterooms situated forward and aft, as well as two doubles and one twin stateroom at midships. The aft master has its own access via a private staircase. All staterooms present with smart TVs and luxurious en suites.","blueprint":{"name":"YAZZ","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::5687d450-fcb0-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::f86865a0-a723-11ef-bfd1-2de653f8b50d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::f4cbbaa0-fcb0-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::f82eb800-a723-11ef-bfd0-2de653f8b50d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::f86a3a60-a723-11ef-bfd2-2de653f8b50d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::25969204094::vessel::4e65d670-fcae-11ee-8a52-5f9ff1fa63b1::assets::138f8ee0-ad7c-11ef-abf0-39a8290a8be6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::2596920409